357
00:20:52,753 --> 00:20:55,130
I know where he'll go and under what name.

358
00:20:59,009 --> 00:21:00,153
- Here's what's gonna happen.
- Here's what's gonna happen.

359
00:21:00,177 --> 00:21:03,055
You are going to do me a couple of favors
