387
00:22:17,171 --> 00:22:18,714
[Hassan] <i>Look, I-I really need to go.</i>

388
00:22:18,797 --> 00:22:22,301
- [chuckles]
- [Zeppo chuckles, blowing raspberries]

389
00:22:22,384 --> 00:22:23,677
[Larry] Let him shit himself.

390
00:22:23,760 --> 00:22:25,321
- [laughs] Hey, tell you what.
- [Hassan] <i>Hello?</i>

391
00:22:25,345 --> 00:22:26,985
He'll be shitting himself in the morning.

392
00:22:27,055 --> 00:22:28,658
